OL,3,CFertility rate in England and Wales
OL,4,Cdrops to new record low
OL,6,FFertility rates have dropped to a
OL,7,Frecord low in England and Wales, ITV
OL,8,FNews' Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,9,FBarry explains the data
OL,11,FFertility rates across England and
OL,12,FWales have dropped to new record low,
OL,13,Fwith the average number of children
OL,14,Fborn to a woman in her lifetime
OL,15,Ffalling to 1.44 per woman in 2023.
OL,17,FWhile fertility rates across the two
OL,18,Fnations has been in overall decline
OL,19,Fsince 2010, the rate is now at its
OL,20,Flowest value since records began in
OL,21,F1938.
