OL,11,FThe data, which also covers stillbirth
OL,12,Frates, said those fell in Wales from a
OL,13,Frate of 4.4 per 1,000 births in 2022
OL,14,Fto 4.0, and stayed the same in England
OL,15,Fat 3.9 stillbirths per 1,000 births.
